{
  "stem": "7094.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But because he worked as an engineer-- and I think he must have worked in Pomerania on the doodlebugs, because he used to travel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't talk about this job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had privileges and had, for one child, a domestic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were trying to-- to-- as a Ukrainian, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were very pleased.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a very good domestic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Um, they-- they-- for my birthday, she would lock herself up and make some clothes for me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had a double life all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this-- and I was brought up-- my grandmother always said, you know, you should always tell the truth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The truth comes out like oil on water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this image of oil, of water coming on the surface all the time, was with me all the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I just had to innovate as I went along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was just-- uh-- confront all the challenges as they came along.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As Berlin was very bombarded, there was a system in Germany that they used to send out whole classrooms to the provinces so that-- with the teacher, so the children would have a little respite from the bombardment.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And her sister was a manageress of a home like this, which is in Crossen an der Oder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so she sent her son with me--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About six?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, and she sent her son with me, because she wanted to keep in family, to work for her sister in this home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then I found myself working in Crossen an der Oder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, well, Crossen an der Oder is now on the borderline, I think about three hours by train-- something like this-- I don't remember exactly-- from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
